				<div class="hvres-meaning"><a href="/whv/翢"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#32738;</span></a><a href="/whv/𢃶"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#139510;</span></a><a href="/whv/𣫟"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#146143;</span></a><a href="/whv/𦇨"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#156136;</span></a><a href="/whv/𦐩"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#156713;</span></a><a href="/whv/𦑢"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#156770;</span></a><a href="/whv/𦒇"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#156807;</span></a><a href="/whv/𦒛"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#156827;</span></a><a href="/whv/𦒞"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#156830;</span></a><a href="/whv/𦒫"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#156843;</span></a><a href="/whv/𦒯"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom" data-tippy-content="Cách viết khác">&#156847;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div>	</div>
